rection is a man under whose feet are placed two hot coals by which his brain boils.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 6561,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":23234,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/06\/15\/never-beloved-hellfire\/","url_meta":{"origin":42232,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Love: Allah never throws His beloved into Hellfire","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 15, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas reported: There was a child on the road as the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, passed through with his companions. When the mother saw the people coming, she was afraid they would trample her son. She quickly gathered him up, saying, \"My son! My son!\" The companions\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":31979,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/12\/malevolent-dishonest-imams\/","url_meta":{"origin":42232,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Ghish: Malevolent and dishonest leaders are in Hellfire","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 12, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever is appointed over the Muslims in any way and he is deceitful to them, he is in the Hellfire.\u201d Source: al-Mu\u2019jam al-Awsat\u0323 3505 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\